@startuml Celery_Worker_Workflow
title Celery Worker Workflow for ARC GitLab Sync

start
:Celery worker process starts;

:Receive task via RabbitMQ broker;
:Retrieve RO-Crate JSON-LD from CouchDB;
:Parse ARC from JSON-LD via ARCtrl library;
:Write ARC scaffold to temporary directory;
:Synchronize ARC scaffold to DataHUB;
:Update metadata in CouchDB;

stop

@enduml
